      <title>强劲的就业报告减轻了美联储下次会议的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/jobs-report-dinger-takes-pressure-off-fed-for-next-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[9月份意外强劲的招聘减少了人们对美国劳动力市场的担忧，从而减轻了美联储的压力，为政策制定者在未来几个月继续以更渐进的速度降息提供了空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/jobs-report-dinger-takes-pressure-off-fed-for-next-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 17:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新调整押注，股市和收益率攀升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就业报告强于预期，迫使交易员们对美联储下次降息幅度的押注有所收敛，美国国债下跌。由于数据凸显了美国经济的韧性并提振了软着陆的希望，股市继续走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑坦德银行支持的 Ebury 开始与伦敦 IPO 投资者进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/santander-backed-ebury-said-to-start-london-ipo-investor-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，西班牙桑坦德银行支持的英国支付集团 Ebury 正开始寻找潜在投资者，计划在伦敦进行首次公开​​募股，目前这家西班牙银行及其创始人正在继续权衡该业务的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/santander-backed-ebury-said-to-start-london-ipo-investor-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 20:51:22 GMT</pubDate>
